snippet.title: Best VGM 604 - Silent Hill : Shattered Memories - When You're Gone
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Silent Hill : Shattered Memories (2009)
When You're Gone
Akira Yamaoka & Mary Elizabeth McGlynn
